                    "body": "No, this issue is not critical.\n\nIf someone uses a language which is not included it will always fall back to the messageid\/default language.\nSo this issue is no blocker and not a must for 1.0.2.\n\nOf course the behaviour is not ok and will be reviewed and fixed.",
